data.description: Welcome HOME! The search is over! Welcome to 22502 Williamschase, a meticulously renovated home that’s ready for your immediate move-in. As you step through the front door, you’ll be captivated by the radiant beauty of the light-filled living room. The kitchen and family room area are destined to become your favorite gathering spot, offering a delightful view of the spacious backyard and firepit area. The convenient half bath downstairs and the enclosed laundry room add to the home’s appeal.    Upstairs, the primary suite is truly massive, and the en-suite bathroom features a stunning, oversized walk-in shower. The upstairs gameroom is perfect for relaxation, and the generously sized guest rooms can easily accommodate your furniture. This home has been renovated to near perfection and won’t stay on the market for long. Don’t miss your chance to schedule an appointment and experience the most beautiful home in the area!
